version_description: THANK YOU – Thanks a bunch for your help in spotting and eradicating those annoying bugs. We resolved the problem with the inability to pass Cable minigame.

HELLO FROM THE QA SIDE! – Thanks to your vigilance, we were able to pinpoint and remove those annoying bugs. They’re in a better place now, and so are all of us. Keep those reviews and emails coming and don’t forget to let us know about any changes you would like to see implemented.
